         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ Sir, — By the last mail, just arrived, I have received a letter from Professor Naudin, ¶  Member of the Institute of France, in which he mentions that the great expectations which Professor Boulay,...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">84.03.09</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">To the Editor of the Australasian Medical Gazette</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found. The text given here is from 'New remedies for hydrophobia', in 'Correspondence', <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Australasian medical gazette</seg>, April 1884, p. 168 (B84.04.02).</p>
               </note>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir, — By the last mail, just arrived, I have received a letter from Professor Naudin,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> Member of the Institute of France, in which he mentions that the great expectations which Professor Boulay, of Paris, from the communications of Dr. Pereira, of Lisbon, set on garlic as a remedy in hydrophobia, have by some recent experiments, published in the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Comptes Rendus</seg>,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gibier (1884) was read at the meeting of the </seg>
                     <seg style="">Académie des Sciences, Paris,</seg>
                     <seg style=""> held on 7 January 1884.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> not been realized. </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The use of pilocarpin proved equally unreliable in hydrophobia, but arsenic, so Professor Naudin says, holds out more hope, as dogs suffering from rabies show immunity to small quantities of arsenic. </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">As yet eucalyptus oil seems never to have been tried in that horrid disease. </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Yours, &amp;c.,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>FERD. VON MUELLER. </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, March 9. </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
